                                                </a></div></div></div><div class="modal-item"><div class="modal-item-flex-container"><div class="modal-image"><figure class="featured_investment_logo"><img class="link_image" src="https://www.revelstokecapital.com//app/uploads/2019/12/carrus-logo-768x542.jpg" alt="Carrus" width="400"></figure></div><div class="modal-body">
