                                                    <h2 class="featured_investment_title">CEI Vision Partners</h2>
                                                    <p class="featured_investment_text">CEI Vision Partners (“CVP”), based in Cincinnati, Ohio, is a management services organization formed in partnership with Cincinnati Eye Institute, a premiere ophthalmology practice in the Midwest with a national reputation for providing the highest quality eye care in the industry. CVP provides comprehensive eye care services and has physicians across all major sub-specialties.</p></div></div></div><div class="modal-item"><div class="modal-item-flex-container"><div class="modal-image"><figure class="featured_investment_logo"><img class="link_image" src="https://www.revelstokecapital.com//app/uploads/CM_health-partners_Final_tiny-768x542.png" alt="ClareMedica Health Partners" width="400"></figure></div><div class="modal-body">
