                                                    <p class="featured_investment_text">ClareMedica Health Partners provides and coordinates comprehensive value-based health care services for Medicare Advantage members and other customers through a network of employed and affiliated physicians. Headquartered in Miami Lakes, FL, ClareMedica delivers accountable, value-based care for all health care stakeholders by employing a patient-centric care model that provides better care for patients.</p><a class="featured_investment_website" href="http://www.claremedica.com/" target="_blank">
